@samskillman unfortunately it looks like `install_requires` is not compatible with numpy.distutils.

I'm still looking at this, but I think the only way to access that functionality would be to use setuptools.setup instead, which it looks like would require retooling our entire distribution method...

I guess we'll just need to add thingking as a hard dependency? I'm a little sad we can't use install_requires so I'm going to continue looking at this today - maybe there's a workaround.
